data.description: Welcome to this stunning and meticulously maintained master-on-main home that effortlessly blends comfort and style. Step inside to discover the luxurious garden tub in the master bathroom, offering a tranquil retreat within your own space. The charm continues with a brick front and sides, complemented by a recently updated rocking chair covered front porch featuring new porch stairs, cable railing, and gate system. Enjoy the outdoors on the new back deck or the expansive yard surrounding this residence. Inside, revel in the beauty of a cozy fireplace and new durable wood-like vinyl flooring throughout, creating a seamless and elegant aesthetic. The home boasts a newer roof from 2019, a new heating and cooling unit, and a two-car garage for added convenience. The basement garage hosts two partially finished and climate-controlled bedrooms, offering flexibility for additional living space or a return to garage functionality. Revel in modern living with a separate dining area, and appreciate the contemporary touches of newly updated electric lights and wiring, new ceiling fans in all bedrooms, and new lighting fixtures throughout the interior and exterior. The kitchen is a chef's delight with a newer Samsung double door refrigerator, a new water heater, and a newer microwave from 2018. Practical amenities abound, including a newer Samsung washer and dryer from 2020, ensuring your laundry needs are met with efficiency. The property comes complete with a new mailbox and post, as well as delightful extras such as a zip-line tire swing and a treehouse for added outdoor enjoyment. The seller's generosity extends to leaving extra hardware, solar lights, paint, stain, sheetrock, wood conditioner, and more, providing you with everything you need to make this house your dream home. Don't miss the chance to experience the perfect blend of modern comfort and classic charm in this immaculate residence.
